{"id":"baalim","term":"Baalim","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Plural of Baal; images of the god Baal (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Judges 2:11\">Judg. 2:11</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Samuel 7:4\">1 Sam. 7:4</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Judges 2:11","1 Samuel 7:4"]}